                         C H R O N O   Q U E S T 
                                (Psygnosis)

1922: THE CHATEAU.

DROP LETTER - EXAMINE URN - TAKE CARD(A) - E - EXAMINE BALL ON SHELF - TAKE
BALL  -  W  -  USE BALL ON LEFT POST - UP - EXAMINE CARPET - TAKE CARD(B) -
EXAMINE  STATUE  - TAKE KEY - USE KEY ON KEYHOLE ON CHEST - EXAMINE CHEST -
TAKE  GLOVES  -  NE - EXAMINE PILLOW - TAKE CARD(C) - LOOK UNDER BED - TAKE
GRAPNEL  AND  ROPE  -  OPEN  RIGHT BEDSIDE CABINET - EXAMINE CABINET - TAKE
SHEET  OF  PAPER  -  SW - DOWN - W - N - OPEN CUPBOARD UNDER SINK - EXAMINE
CUPBOARD  - (you reveal a chest with a dial) - USE PIECE OF PAPER ON DIAL -
TAKE LIGHTER - (cash is not needed!) - TAKE BOTTLE - S - E - NE - (Dark!) -
LIGHT  LIGHTER  -  UP  - E - TAKE CANDLE - LIGHT CANDLE - UNLIGHT LIGHTER -
EXAMINE  BIBLE  -  TAKE  CARD(D)  - W - DOWN - DOWN - E - EXAMINE DIAGRAM -
(diagram  of  'Explora') - EXAMINE RIGHT PICTURE - PUSH SWITCH - (DO NOT go
through  the  door  yet as there is an electrical current which needs to be
turned  off!)  -  W  -  UP - SW - DROP GLOVES - TAKE BALL - (current is now
disconnected)  -  DROP  BALL  - TAKE GLOVES - NE - DOWN - E - DROP CANDLE -
OPEN  LEFT  DRAWER  - EXAMINE DRAWER - TAKE FUSES - N - (you are now in the
Laboratory  with the Time Machine) - EXAMINE BOX ON WALL - USE FUSES ON BOX
-  PULL SWITCH - (Left of box) - UP - (into the Machine) - SHOW PANEL - USE
CARD A IN SLOT - (you are now transported to the Prehistoric Zone).

33172 BC: PREHISTORIC ZONE.

(Note:-  If you wander around for too long in this zone, you will be killed
by Elephants!).

DOWN - E - EXAMINE HUT - TAKE DRY GRASS - NE - E - EXAMINE FIRE - (piece of
wood) - LIGHT LIGHTER - LIGHT GRASS - DROP GRASS ON FIRE - TAKE WOOD - (you
now  have  a  torch)  - DROP LIGHTER - E - S - EXAMINE BOWL - TAKE PIECE OF
CARD  -  N - W - DROP TORCH - TAKE A SMALL ROCK - W - SW - EXAMINE ENTRANCE
OF  HUT  -  TAKE  BONE  -  W  -  UP  - SHOW PANEL - PRESS ON - (back to the
Laboratory)  -  SHOW  PANEL  - USE CARD B IN SLOT - (you are transported to
India).

1605 AD: INDIA.

(Note:- Watch out for tigers!).

DOWN  -  W  -  N - USE GLOVE - TAKE HAND - (the Leper tells you to take the
paper to the Mahouts who will lead you to the sacred spring) - (He asks you
to  get the Water of Recovery to cure his leprosy) - TAKE PAPER - S - E - E
-  NE  -  DROP  PAPER  - UP - (you are riding on an elephant and taken to a
temple) - DOWN - E - USE BOTTLE - TAKE WATER - W - UP - (taken back) - DOWN
-  SW  -  W  -  W  - N - DROP BOTTLE - TAKE KEY - S - E - N - USE KEY - N -
EXAMINE ENVELOPE - TAKE PIECE OF CARD - (don't bother with the water) - S -
W  -  W - TAKE SCROLL - (don't waste time now or you will be stabbed in the
back  by the Fakir!!) - E - E - UP - SHOW PANEL - PRESS ON - (Laboratory) -
READ SCROLL - ("Top - Top Left - Top Right - Top Right") - SHOW PANEL - USE
CARD C IN SLOT - (you are now transported to Egypt).




1100 BC: EGYPT.

(Note:- Be Careful! You might get run over!!).

DOWN  -  NE  - (a pedestrian crossing!) - N - N - EXAMINE STONE JUST TO THE
RIGHT OF THE BUSH - TAKE AMULET - (remember the scroll?!) - PRESS TOP STONE
-  PRESS  TOP  LEFT STONE - PRESS TOP RIGHT STONE - PRESS TOP RIGHT STONE -
(Door  opens)  - N - N - DROP AMULET - (to get rid of the snakes) - N - W -
USE GRAPNEL AND ROPE - UP - EXAMINE LEVERS - PUSH LEVERS 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 1 -
EXAMINE  PAINTING - TAKE PIECE OF CARD - TAKE RING - DOWN - E - S - S - S -
S  -  S - SW - UP - SHOW PANEL - PRESS ON - (Laboratory) - SHOW PANEL - USE
CARD D IN SLOT - (you are now transported to Mexico).

750 AD: MEXICO.

(Note:- You could die of thirst if you stay here too long!).

DOWN  -  E - E - EXAMINE PLANT UNDER TREE - TAKE NECKLACE - W - W - W - W -
EXAMINE  WARRIOR  - USE NECKLACE ON HIS RIGHT FOREARM - (he draws a diagram
and  tells you to go to the three stones and follow his way) - NE - NE - NE
-  EXAMINE HUT - TURN KNOB - TAKE KEY - W - W - W - (at the Three Stones) -
NE  -  NE  -  NE - N - N - NW - NW - NE - E - EXAMINE MOUND OF GRASS -  USE
RING IN HOLE - UP - UP - (picture of a doorway appears) - USE BONE IN RIGHT
HAND  SLOT - (this prevents a portcullis from dropping down on you when you
go up!) - UP - USE KEY ON CHEST - EXAMINE CHEST - TAKE PIECE OF CARD - (the
four pieces now become ONE CARD!!) - DOWN - W - SW - SE - SE - S - S - SW -
SW  - SW - S - S - S - E - UP - SHOW PANEL - PRESS ON - (Laboratory) - SHOW
PANEL - INSERT CARD IN SLOT - (you are now transported to your final Zone -
The Future!!).

2125 AD: THE FUTURE.

DOWN - PUSH BUTTON ON CONTROL PANEL - E - (Guard appears in the doorway!) -
HIT  FACE  (WITH)  ROCK - EXAMINE GUARD - TAKE SUIT - TAKE GUN - TAKE KEY -
USE  SUIT  -  N  -  W  -  W  - N - OPEN CUPBOARD ABOVE RIGHT SEAT - EXAMINE
CUPBOARD - TAKE TORCH - S - E - E - E - E - S - PRESS BUTTON ON GENERATOR -
PRESS  BUTTON ON DESK - (a diagram of a machine appears showing position of
fuses) - N - N - N - (the door to the North leads to Space.......there is a
space-suit in the right hand cupboard which you can wear and go outside for
ONE  MOVE.....if  you  go  any  further  you  become lost in Space.....this
procedure  is  not  necessary so leave this exit and the suit alone!) - W -
OPEN  BOX  ON TOP LEFT OF MACHINE - EXAMINE BOX - TAKE FUSES - (the machine
shuts  down) - E - S - S - E - USE KEY IN HOLE ON BOX...................the
door  opens.......you  find  Richard  at  last!!........your  Father's vile
servant....he throws himself at your mercy and begs you to take him back to
his time period.

                        YOU HAVE PROVED YOURSELF AS
                           A MASTER  ADVENTURER!
                       THIS IS ONLY THE BEGINNING...


